***** WARNING *****

The delivery of 1.0.16-RELEASE of this framework will be the final source code commit that will be made on SourceForge; all further updates can be found at the following address:

https://bitbucket.org/CoherentLogic/coherent-logic-foundation-data-model

***** WARNING *****

This project contains code which is the foundation for several data models -- at the moment these include:

* The Coherent Logic FRED Client -- https://sourceforge.net/projects/clfredclient/
* The Coherent Logic World Bank Client -- https://sourceforge.net/projects/clwbclient/
* The Coherent Logic USA Spending Client -- https://sourceforge.net/projects/clusaspendingclient/
